{"tid":1489490,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港犯案率持續下降 代表緊警察做到野？","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T04:15:26.000Z","uid":46879,"like":41,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"461a2edbcbfcf2ceac01af414c9bba3cc331a1ab","tid":1489490,"uid":46879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"首先睇下總犯案唔由2009年到2019年嘅變化先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yqXsQEA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyqXsQEA.jpg&h=0cb62c91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有三點大家要留意到:<br />\n1.犯案數目係要警察開簿先計<br />\n2.犯案數由09年到18年跌左近三成<br />\n3.破案率維持係40%-45%<br />\n<br />\n單睇呢張圖 可以有個小結<br />\n1.警方破案總數亦係10年間下降左三成<br />\n2.警察開簿量亦少左三成<br />\n<br />\n值得注意嘅係 根據統計署 <br />\n香港人口由2008年嘅695.8萬人<br />\n增加至2017年739.2萬<br />\n<br />\n係人口增加但罪案量減少嘅情況下<br />\n只有兩個可能性做得到<br />\n1.實際犯罪數量其實持續上升 但警方因種種原因未能開簿 e.g. 偵辦能力下降 以開簿以外嘅方法處理罪犯<br />\n2.實際犯罪數量減少<br />\n<br />\n如果係前者 明顯犯罪量減少不單止唔係因為警方嘅努力 而係因為警隊能力/質素下降<br />\n<br />\n如果係後者 犯罪誘因減少令犯罪量下降 但並無實際數據證明警方同降低犯罪誘因 相反社教化/滿足基本經濟需要等等嘅社會因素同犯罪誘因減少可有直接關係<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦 你認為香港罪案減少嘅原因係因為<br />\n警察能力問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港真係好太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c0b8fee2106429df9cd2c1931e0f64113952e3","tid":1489490,"uid":264871,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:36:21.000Z","msg":"只係代表佢地唔做野"},{"pid":"a917cef61b5d53a7a71562fa323d4a7e40f0e2f6","tid":1489490,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d51c522752ce98cfd42bbeba40a70df09d8055","tid":1489490,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"養埋班垃圾"},{"pid":"e7b9e0103dd8662c473733d1866245a958ab7fd7","tid":1489490,"uid":252960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:29.000Z","msg":"你on9嗎 問呢個問題 休班警唔計 黑社會唔計 數字咪少咗一大截"},{"pid":"c6df1a23c52ad1a5a71b44604036a8496e506a83","tid":1489490,"uid":22707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"你個poll 寫警察之後仲要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我黎手俾左負評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c432867b2170fde0f2b83fec70523692b6528de","tid":1489490,"uid":83378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"下下都叫你唔追究 唔開file 犯案率緊係低"},{"pid":"63e8e95d471537ec0678b3f7fac5f05f95d73b27","tid":1489490,"uid":22707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c6df1a23c52ad1a5a71b44604036a8496e506a83","tid":1489490,"uid":22707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:37:50.000Z","msg":"你個poll 寫警察之後仲要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我黎手俾左負評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不如開過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:38:40.000Z","msg":"香港真係好太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察能力問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2170b7cff6b41be3ce8126941f51465e7e44dfce","tid":1489490,"uid":189430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"係咪都叫你唔好追究<br />\n話好麻煩<br />\n話冇得搞<br />\n話冇得告<br />\n咁咪唔使開簿囉<br />\n成班社會寄生蟲<br />\n啊唔係<br />\n係癌細胞"},{"pid":"080b66a6981f2160e6e722fc53818785327967aa","tid":1489490,"uid":223639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:40:08.000Z","msg":"罪案率下降可能喺因為市民唔信警察，寧願私了都唔洗你幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8102f2374831ecffe5c340ae971fbc59227538","tid":1489490,"uid":102982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:40:12.000Z","m